don't shave theirs.

01:28.068 --> 01:29.501
Eh, huh?

01:34.074 --> 01:35.507
Stop!

01:38.578 --> 01:44.016
It was somewhere right along here
that I lost all interest in life.

01:44.084 --> 01:46.518
Aha! It was
right here.

01:46.586 --> 01:50.022
This is where I saw
Dolores Reineke...

01:50.090 --> 01:52.024
and fat Marvin!

01:54.594 --> 01:56.528
Why, Dolores?

01:56.596 --> 01:58.029
Why?

01:59.099 --> 02:00.532
They're
married now.

02:01.601 --> 02:03.466
See what I
saved you from?

02:03.537 --> 02:07.473
If I hadn't told you, you never
would have followed them out here.

02:07.541 --> 02:11.341
You made me lose
all interest in life,

02:11.378 --> 02:12.936
and I'm grateful.

02:18.151 --> 02:22.986
My brother said he saw
you and Nancy, Moocher.

02:23.056 --> 02:24.489
When?

02:24.558 --> 02:25.991
Uh... last Friday.

02:26.059 --> 02:27.492
Well, it wasn't me.

02:27.561 --> 02:29.995
I'm not seeing
her anymore.

02:38.071 --> 02:40.505
I kind of
miss school.

02:40.574 --> 02:42.508
This will be
the first time

02:42.576 --> 02:45.511
no one will ask us
to write a theme

02:45.579 --> 02:47.513
- About how we spent our summer.
- Yeah.

02:50.484 --> 02:52.975
When you're 16,
they call it sweet 16.

02:53.086 --> 02:56.021
At 18, you can drink,
vote, and see dirty movies.

02:56.089 --> 02:59.718
What the hell do you get to do
when you're 19?

03:01.495 --> 03:03.292
You leave home.

03:03.363 --> 03:05.331
My dad said

03:05.432 --> 03:08.765
Jesus never went further
than 50 miles from his home.

03:08.835 --> 03:11.303
Look what
happened to him.

03:11.371 --> 03:12.804
Whoo!

03:17.544 --> 03:19.239
Hey, man,
this feels great!

03:19.312 --> 03:20.745
Ahh!
Come on in!

03:22.549 --> 03:24.449
Hey, come on in,
Dave.

03:24.551 --> 03:27.452
I read where
this Italian coach said

03:27.554 --> 03:30.455
it's no good to swim
right after a race.

03:30.557 --> 03:33.253
Who's swimming?
I'm taking a leak.

